---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

---

<Layout title="Katrinah.io | Home">
	<main>
		<h1>Hi! I'm <span class="text-gradient">Katrina</span>.</h1>
		<p><i>I'm a Technologist specializing in technology security and compliance. 💜</i></p>
		<p class="intro">
			Join me on my journey as I shift my focus from the world of design systems and coding to the dynamic field of cybersecurity. I'll share my insights, experiences, and challenges along the way. I'll also explore how my background in design and programming might inform this career shift. 🥳
		</p>
		<div>
			<p>To Do:</p>
			<ul>
				<li><s>Say goodbye 👋🏾 to using Gatsby &amp; Gatsby Cloud. <a href="https://www.behance.net/gallery/124201631/Personal-Website/modules/706890577" target="_blank">Previous design.</a></s></li>
				<li><s>Set up Astro and deploy to Netlify</s></li>
				<li>Create the design system... because why not!</li>
				<li>Design the website</li>				
				<li>Write and publish blog posts</li>
				<li>Coninuously upload/publish</li>
				<li>Maybe even <a href="https://twitter.com/TrinaBHu">tweet</a> about it too!</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div>
			<p>05/15/24 - A little career shift last year, intro update and domain forwarding. A proper design and blog posts coming soon.😉</p>
		</div>
		<div>
			<p>09/15/23 - It's been pretty busy over here so this endeavor has been on pause for a bit. I did manage to upgrade to Astro 3.0 this week. I've also started a couple of online classes around design, design systems and <a href="https://astro.build/" target="_blank">Astro</a> of course!</p>
		</div>
		<div>
			You can follow these updates on <a href="https://github.com/katrinah">Github</a>!
		</div>

	</main>
</Layout>

<style>
	main {
		margin: auto;
		padding: 1.5rem;
		max-width: 60ch;
	}
	h1 {
		font-size: 3rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		margin: 0;
	}
	.text-gradient {
		background-image: var(--accent-gradient);
		-webkit-background-clip: text;
		-webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
		background-size: 400%;
		background-position: 0%;
	}
	.intro {
		line-height: 1.6;
		margin: 1rem 0;
		border: 1px solid rgba(var(--accent), 25%);
		background-color: white;
		padding: 1rem;
		border-radius: 0.4rem;
	}
</style>
